---

<section class="px-4">
  <div class="container min-h-screen mx-auto lg:flex items-center gap-4 w-fit ">
    <div class="w-full lg:w-1/2">
      <p class="text-sm font-medium text-lime-600">404 error</p>
      <h1 class="mt-3 text-2xl font-semibold md:text-3xl">
        No contamos con esta pagina
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-4">Lo sentimos, la pagina que buscas no existe.</p>

      <div class="flex items-center mt-6 gap-x-3">
        <button
          class="w-1/2 px-5 py-2 text-sm tracking-wide text-white transition-colors duration-200 bg-lime-600 rounded-lg shrink-0 sm:w-auto hover:bg-lime-600 dark:hover:bg-lime-600 "
        >
          <a href="/volcancafe/">Regresar al inicio</a>
        </button>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-10 space-y-6">
        <div>
          <a
            href="/volcancafe/tours"
            class="inline-flex items-center text-sm text-lime-600 gap-x-2 hover:underline"
          >
            <span>Tours</span>

            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              stroke-width="1.5"
              stroke="currentColor"
              class="w-5 h-5 rtl:rotate-180"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                d="M17.25 8.25L21 12m0 0l-3.75 3.75M21 12H3"></path>
            </svg>
          </a>

          <p class="mt-2 text-sm">Busca alguna aventura.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <a
            href="/volcancafe/cabanas"
            class="inline-flex items-center text-sm text-lime-600 gap-x-2 hover:underline"
          >
            <span>Cabanañas</span>

            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              stroke-width="1.5"
              stroke="currentColor"
              class="w-5 h-5 rtl:rotate-180"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                d="M17.25 8.25L21 12m0 0l-3.75 3.75M21 12H3"></path>
            </svg>
          </a>

          <p class="mt-2 text-sm">Descansa en alguna de nuestras cabañas.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <a
            href="/volcancafe/contacto"
            class="inline-flex items-center text-sm text-lime-600 gap-x-2 hover:underline"
          >
            <span>Contacto</span>

            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              stroke-width="1.5"
              stroke="currentColor"
              class="w-5 h-5 rtl:rotate-180"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                d="M17.25 8.25L21 12m0 0l-3.75 3.75M21 12H3"></path>
            </svg>
          </a>

          <p class="mt-2 text-sm">
            Ponte en contacto con nosotros, atenderemos cualquier duda.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="relative w-full mt-8 lg:w-1/2 lg:mt-0">
      <img
        class="w-full lg:h-[32rem] h-80 md:h-96 rounded-lg object-cover shadow-md"
        src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1508881598441-324f3974994b?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=MnwxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8&auto=format&fit=crop&w=2070&q=80"
        alt=""
        loading="lazy"
      />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
